snippet.title: Best and funniest squirrel & chipmunk videos - Funny and cute animal compilation
snippet.description:
When I finished this compilation, I was like 'I like squirrels' :P Aren't they so funny and cute? And I also noticed that they are very persistent.  They just don't give up so quickly! Squirrels are awesome! Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
